      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD NIH predictions agree with experimental NIH within 15% at all five calibration operating points.",
      "rationale": "Point-wise comparison of CFD NIH versus experimental NIH at all five operating points shows maximum deviation of 11.3% and mean absolute error of 7.6%. All five points fall within the 15% acceptance band. R²=0.974 and Pearson r=0.987 are cited as additional evidence of agreement quality. Gradation 2 requirement met."
    },
