      "rationale": "The normalized index of hemolysis is the standard regulatory QOI for blood-contacting rotary devices and directly feeds the relative hemolysis index acceptance criterion. The mapping from CFD shear stress history to NIH via the power-law model is well-established in the literature. Gradation 2 requirement met."
    },
    {
