      "rationale": "Validation experiments used the FDA-specified generic centrifugal pump geometry and blood analog fluid under CPB flow rates (2.5–7 L/min) and rotational speeds (2500–4200 RPM) representative of clinical CPB use. Device class, fluid properties, and operating regime are sufficiently similar to the COU to support credibility at MRL 2. Gradation 2 requirement met."
