    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation level for MRL 2. Validation results demonstrate R²=0.974 and Pearson r=0.987 between CFD predictions and experimental hemolysis measurements, and the RH=0.83 at the nominal operating point satisfies the RH<1 acceptance criterion. Six factors were not assessed, consistent with MRL 2 requirements. The credibility evidence is judged sufficient to support the COU decision that the CFD model can identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
